### Deal v2 API Test
### 실행 순서
### 1) ../_env.http 로그인 3개 실행
### 2) ../_common.http 또는 본 파일 [S1]로 dealId 확보
### 3) 조회 -> KPI -> 알림/일정 순서로 실행

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@dealId = 1

### [S1] deal v2 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals?page=0&size=20&sort=lastActivityAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{salesAccessToken}}

> {%
client.test("deal v2 list success", function () {
  client.assert(response.status === 200, "status must be 200");
  client.assert(response.body.result === "SUCCESS", "result must be SUCCESS");
});
if (response.body?.data?.content?.length > 0) {
  const first = response.body.data.content[0];
  if (first.dealId) client.global.set("dealId", first.dealId);
}
%}

### [S2] deal v2 상세 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals/{{dealId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{salesAccessToken}}

### [S3] deal v2 문서 목록 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals/{{dealId}}/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{salesAccessToken}}

### [S4] deal v2 알림 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals/{{dealId}}/notifications
Authorization: Bearer {{salesAccessToken}}

### [S5] deal v2 일정 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals/{{dealId}}/schedules?fromAt=2026-03-01T00:00:00&toAt=2026-03-31T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{salesAccessToken}}

### [S6] deal KPI v2 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals/kpis?fromAt=2026-03-01T00:00:00&toAt=2026-03-31T23:59:59
Authorization: Bearer {{adminAccessToken}}

### [F1] 비인증 KPI 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals/kpis?fromAt=2026-03-01T00:00:00&toAt=2026-03-31T23:59:59

### [F2] 잘못된 날짜 범위
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/deals?fromAt=2026-03-31T23:59:59&toAt=2026-03-01T00:00:00
Authorization: Bearer {{salesAccessToken}}
